long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Doodle Jump - Unblocked is a popular arcade game available as a Chrome extension. Take control of a cute, bouncing character and guide it as high as possible on a never-ending platform. Tilt your device or use the keyboard to navigate through various obstacles, including monsters and UFOs. Collect power-ups and avoid falling off the platforms to achieve the highest score. With its simple controls, charming doodle-style graphics, and addictive gameplay, Doodle Jump Unblocked offers endless fun and challenge for players of all ages. Jump your way to the top and set new records in this addictive Chrome extension game.

If you want play more game, press Unblocked Games to find more games on our website: https://doodlejump.net
